                     <origDate calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1803">Internally dated to the year <foreign xml:lang="ta">tuntu<unclear>mī</unclear></foreign>, that is, <foreign xml:lang="ta">tuntupi</foreign> of the Jovian cycle, that is, CE 1802-1803, 1742-1741, etc. See colophon (U2, <locus facs="253">f128r5</locus>).
